{"tid":1535120,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港要贏，必須要去政黨化","createTime":"2019-09-03T08:46:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T14:10:15.000Z","uid":234352,"like":48,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"4df27a830f3cc302e2cb552aa1738594b6ea8b8e","tid":1535120,"uid":234352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T08:46:27.000Z","msg":"香港要贏，必須要<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">去政黨化</span></span>，拒絕任何人做政治代理，不妥協，不談判。<br />\n<br />\n我好老實講，呢一刻仲諗住11月區議會選舉的人，請問心問良知，有無諗過已經獻出鮮血身體生命的義士，他們用生命衝擊立法會，象徵的就是<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">議會失效，人民自救</span></span>。你覺得議會仍需要泛民主派去抗衡建制派的無恥？不需要了，我們已經民智開花，很多人的政治智慧甚至比從政者高，既然我們不吃831政改方案呢舊屎，何解要繼續食區議會投票呢舊屎？<br />\n<br />\n我不是說不需要泛民，但那是得到真普選之後的事。現在著眼投票？我真的好怕，好怕有一班人真的見民主派大勝就收貨了。那些於獄中的人呢？又要等到出年立法會選舉再救？還是已變成condom？然而不要忘了中共清算的能力，你覺得習總會給你一年時間重整民主派於議會的勢力？大家心裡有數。<br />\n<br />\n我好希望唔好再有人諗住區選，努力將心血放於國際文宣，同時將去政黨化的概念帶到國際，讓國際知道北京已失去對香港的管治權，同時歡迎所有政黨議員以香港人的身份，一齊向國際發出SOS訊號，讓香港的問題不能以內政解決，交由國際公論。香港沒有軍隊，沒有軍事訓練，如繼續被中共軍閥式統治，只靠勇武派是不足夠，我們必須讓國際知道香港人清晰的求救訊號，讓聯合國支持美國解放香港，這是國際外交的借力打力，也是對義士的最大助攻。<br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山，不是只各自努力，大家手足，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">榮辱與共</span></span>。"},{"pid":"851c5c12e39a17b023dba15c2821b24c7cc3e777","tid":1535120,"uid":234352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T08:48:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">議會失效，人民自救</span></span>"},{"pid":"f9818be84ef27f611dabe1b9dd5aab090cb5a3bf","tid":1535120,"uid":54303,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T08:50:23.000Z","msg":"拒絕政棍騎劫<br />\n人民訴求優先"},{"pid":"4d79be945def20484baf8f811fdfda370700505e","tid":1535120,"uid":266362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T08:50:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">想大個仔獨立必睇</span></span></span></strong><br />\n［召喚攬炒巴] 星球級反擊！香港最後本錢 VS 赤獸<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1529054\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1529054</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n請幫推以下post！<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\"><strong><ins><span style=\"color: violet;\">香港人一定要知！</span></ins></strong></span></span>一定一定要睇！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: navy;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">香港史實在此！勿做港豬！想贏就入嚟！</span></span></span></span></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"7a6302d0665573c0ecef72024369315edea38313","tid":1535120,"uid":234352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T08:51:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">議會失效，人民自救</span></span>"},{"pid":"f306e2ecb1452c5489244cb569c8aaf4164c68a7","tid":1535120,"uid":284264,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T08:52:51.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">議會抗爭都係抗爭既一種<br />\n點解今次送中林鄭最初可以咁囂張？<br />\n因為議會失去左否決權呀！<br />\n<br />\n議員幫手掩護示威者有用架！<br />\n議員被拉外國即刻報導呀！<br />\n<br />\n不推文回覆</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"fe1cf2dc6b2c7fbf7d020d4f1ff22f360b12a406","tid":1535120,"uid":234352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T08:55:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"27891a5b58fabb4a3bd2b9c0762fd83a098e051a","tid":1535120,"uid":234352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T08:55:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ec3b28e55e6ad8be68d98872f7c9910074b622ea","tid":1535120